i.org/10.1016/S0003-4975(96)00927-7">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8993268/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Radical+resection+of+radiation-induced+sarcoma+of+the+chest+wall%3A+report+of+15+cases&amp;author=AR+Chapelier&amp;author=EA+Bacha&amp;author=VT+de+Montpreville&amp;publication_year=1997&amp;journal=Ann+Thorac+Surg&amp;pages=214-219&amp;doi=10.1016%2FS0003-4975%2896%2900927-7&amp;pmid=8993268">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">82.</div><div id="r82" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Fineberg S, Rosen PP. Cutaneous angiosarcoma and atypical vascular lesions of the skin and breast after radiation therapy for breast carcinoma. <em>Am J Clin Pathol</em> 1994;102(6):757–763.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/ajcp/102.6.757">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/7801888/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Cutaneous+angiosarcoma+and+atypical+vascular+lesions+of+the+skin+and+breast+after+radiation+therapy+for+breast+carcinoma&amp;author=S+Fineberg&amp;author=PP+Rosen&amp;publication_year=1994&amp;journal=Am+J+Clin+Pathol&amp;pages=757-763&amp;doi=10.1093%2Fajcp%2F102.6.757&amp;pmid=7801888">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">83.</div><div id="r83" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Tateishi U, Gladish GW, Kusumoto M, et al. Chest wall tumors: radiologic findings and pathologic correlation. II. malignant tumors. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2003;23(6):1491–1508.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="h